# AtlasIT Development Rules

## 1. Project Structure Rules

### 1.1 Architecture
- Maintain modular microservices architecture with clear separation of concerns
- Each service must be self-contained with its own package.json and dependencies
- Use Cloudflare Workers for serverless deployment
- Follow consistent file structure across all services:
  ```
  service/
  ├── src/
  │   ├── handlers/     # Request handlers
  │   ├── models/       # Data models
  │   ├── services/     # Business logic
  │   └── utils/        # Helper functions
  ├── tests/            # Test files
  ├── wrangler.toml     # Cloudflare config
  └── package.json
  ```

### 1.2 Service Organization
- Onboarding: AI-guided tenant setup and configuration
- Marketplace: App/integration discovery and management
- Auth: Multi-tenant authentication and OIDC/SAML support
- Orchestrator: Event processing and workflow management
- API Manager: Request routing and security enforcement
- Applications: SaaS integrations and custom solutions

